| 8 byte    | 8 byte            | 8 byte            | 32 byte   | .../
+-----------+-------------------+-------------------+-----------+-----
| length    | identification0   | identification1   | md5sum    | .../
----------------------------------------------------------------------`

Notes:
Every client has an identification.
`length', `identification0', `identification1' are hexadecimal-character.

